  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Greed for speed in Yeet Thyself! An endless runner where the faster you go, the higher your score multiplier. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grapple skylands and glide between them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With enough speed you can break through skylands to gain extra points! But be careful, at slow speeds, they will stop you.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.poster.avif?t=1742776111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.webm?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.mp4?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach high enough in the sky to enter the wind zone. This will give you a great boost of speed!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.poster.avif?t=1742776111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.webm?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.mp4?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look before you shoot! One miss with your grapple could leave you in the depths below, ending your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/558753b5c216a20430c5b7dbcfd0dad4.poster.avif?t=1742776111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/558753b5c216a20430c5b7dbcfd0dad4.webm?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/558753b5c216a20430c5b7dbcfd0dad4.mp4?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Greed for speed in Yeet Thyself! An endless runner where the faster you go, the higher your score multiplier. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grapple skylands and glide between them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With enough speed you can break through skylands to gain extra points! But be careful, at slow speeds, they will stop you.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.poster.avif?t=1742776111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.webm?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/18e5b5f36cd376ee6b0f4f7fe7a17cfe.mp4?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach high enough in the sky to enter the wind zone. This will give you a great boost of speed!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.poster.avif?t=1742776111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.webm?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356160/extras/eb3603d338e4c7f1c55bfb07eccfcd6f.mp4?t=1742776111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look before you shoot! One miss with your grapple could leave you in the depths below, ending your run.</p><p 